Class Summary

TupleSerialization Class TupleSerialization is an implementation of Hadoop's Serialization interface.
TupleSerialization.SerializationElementReader  
TupleSerialization.SerializationElementWriter  
TupleSerializationProps Class TupleSerializationProps is a fluent interface for building properties to be passed to a FlowConnector before creating new Flow instances.
 

Annotation Types Summary
SerializationToken Annotation SerializationToken enables TupleInputStream and TupleOutputStream to substitute Integer values for a class name when writing out nested objects inside a Tuple.
